title: Patty
text: Purchased many items for my sister's Bachelorette party. Everything I bought was I'm great quality and true to picture and description. Nothing looked cheap. My items were received within a week of ordering. I love them packaging. You can tell a lot of care goes into it. Will definitely shop here again and recommend to others!!!
